<section
    class="contact-section w-full min-h-[30vh] sm:min-h-[40vh] md:min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 bg-[#141414] flex items-center justify-center"
>
    <div
        class="w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center text-center md:-translate-x-5"
    >
        <h2
            class="contact-title text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6 text-white tracking-tight"
        >
            Un projet ? <span class="text-[#4A5D23]">Parlons-en</span> !
        </h2>

        <p
            class="contact-subtitle text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl text-[#B8B8B8] mb-6 sm:mb-8 md:mb-10 lg:mb-12 font-medium max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl px-2 sm:px-4 md:px-0"
        >
            Nous sommes à votre écoute pour concrétiser vos idées et propulser
            votre business.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-6">
            <a
                href="/contact"
                class="contact-cta-uniform group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-48 px-0 py-3 md:py-4 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-[#4A5D23] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#6b755a] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(74,93,35,0.3)] whitespace-nowrap no-underline"
            >
                <span
                    class="relative text-white font-medium text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase transition-colors"
                >
                    Nous contacter
                </span>
            </a>
            <a
                href="tel:+33169127210"
                class="contact-cta-uniform group relative inline-flex items-center justify-center w-48 px-0 py-3 md:py-4 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-[#E07A1F] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-[#C86618] hover:shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(224,122,31,0.4)] whitespace-nowrap no-underline"
            >
                <span
                    class="relative text-white font-medium text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase transition-colors flex items-center gap-2"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        width="20"
                        height="20"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        class="inline-block"
                    >
                        <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Appeler
                </span>
            </a>
        </div>

<style>
.contact-cta-uniform {
    width: 12rem;
    min-width: 12rem;
    max-width: 12rem;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-left: 0;
    padding-right: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
}
@media (max-width: 640px) {
    .contact-cta-uniform {
        width: 100%;
        min-width: 0;
        max-width: none;
    }
}
</style>
    </div>
</section>
